snippet.title: v8.1 Drumming in New Resolutions Trailer - Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
Honkai Impact 3rd v8.1 Drumming in New Resolutions coming soon! Kiana's new S-rank battlesuit Ba-Dum! Fiery Wishing Star debuts!
Part 2 Main Story Chapter VII Interlude: To None May God Pray, featured event Ongoing: Make-A-Wish Fest!, Celebration Lobby 2025, and more exciting content to be released! Stay tuned!
Voice Artists:
Senadina: Minori Suzuki
Leylah: Yuki Nakashima
Litost: Kenji Hamada
Theresa Apocalypse: Yukari Tamura
Kiana Kaslana: Rie Kugimiya
Rice Cake: Rie Kugimiya
